## Benefits

- **Fastest bug creation** - Skips template selection
- **Auto-categorized** - Immediately tagged as bug
- **Immediate fix** - Option to start working right away
- **Rich context** - Claude generates comprehensive bug reports
- **Team visibility** - All bugs tracked in Linear

## Configuration

Uses your Linear workflow configuration:
- **Team**: {{linear.teamName}} ({{linear.teamKey}})
- **Template**: Bug Report (automatic)
- **Default Status**: "To Do"
- **Priority**: Normal (can be changed after creation)

